- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on Android security and vulnerability detection tools. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper discusses the systemization of knowledge of Android security mechanisms. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper deals with the security of a mobile platform. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possibility as the paper discusses the impact of smartphones and their vulnerabilities on society. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility as the paper discusses open source tools for vulnerability detection on the Android platform.
